2011-07-11T00:46:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/universal-vision-june-sales-rise-11-12-table-3218-tt.html
UNIVERSAL VISION said unconsolidated sales
in June rose 11.12% to NT$60,847,000 from NT$54,758,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             60,847           54,758    
YOY%              11.12%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            396,668          314,336    
YOY%              26.19% 
=================================================================
 